@startuml
[*] --> Scheduled
Scheduled --> InProgress : session-status-sync detects start
InProgress --> Completed : session-status-sync detects end
Scheduled --> Cancelled : teacher cancels
InProgress --> Cancelled : teacher cancels
Scheduled --> AttendanceMaterialized : sync creates default rows
InProgress --> AttendanceRecorded : manual attendance
AttendanceMaterialized --> AttendanceRecorded : teacher updates status
AttendanceRecorded --> AttendanceRecorded : update manual status
AttendanceRecorded --> FeeSynced : sync fee record
FeeSynced --> Completed : session ends
Cancelled --> [*]
Completed --> [*]
@enduml
